snippet: Amelie Mauresmo has revealed the reasons for her coaching split with Andy Murray, explaining they "reached the end" of what they could achieve and he was a "complex" player to work with....
lead_paragraph: Amelie Mauresmo has revealed the reasons for her coaching split with Andy Murray, explaining they "reached the end" of what they could achieve and he was a "complex" player to work with.

headline.print_headline: Mauresmo Explains Coaching Split With 'Complex' Murray
headline.main: Mauresmo Explains Coaching Split With 'Complex' Murray
